```
Root > CampusAdmin > GradeAdmin > Teacher > TeachingAssistant > Student
```

`Role` enum (defined in `shared/src/models/role.rs`) implements `is_higher_or_equal()` method for hierarchy comparison. `Root` has system-global access and skips all tenant checks.

