|----------|-------------|
| User Management | `ManageUsers`, `ViewUsers` |
| Problem Management | `ManageProblems`, `ViewAllProblems`, `SubmitSolution` |
| Contest Management | `ManageContests`, `RegisterContests`, `ViewContestProblems` |
| Class Management | `ManageClasses`, `ManageAssignments`, `GradeSubmissions`, `ViewClassStats` |
| Organization Management | `ManageOrganization`, `ManageCampus` |
| System Management | `ViewLeaderboard`, `ViewStatistics`, `ModerateContent`, `ManageTags`, `ManageSystem`, `ViewLogs`, `ManageApiKeys` |

