## 10. Worker Heartbeat System

Judge workers report status every 10 seconds via `POST /internal/worker/heartbeat` (using `X-Worker-Secret` auth, not JWT).

**Heartbeat Payload:**

```json
{
  "worker_id": "worker-<uuid>",
  "active_judgements": 2,
  "total_processed": 1042,
  "avg_wait_ms": 350,
  "redis_breaker_state": "Closed",
  "api_breaker_state": "Closed"
}
```

API stores heartbeat data in Redis with 30s TTL. When TTL expires (3 consecutive missed heartbeats), worker is considered offline and removed from admin monitoring panel.

**Metrics Tracked:**

| Metric | Implementation | Description |
|--------|---------------|-------------|
| `active_judgements` | `AtomicUsize` + RAII `ActiveGuard` | Increment on creation, decrement on destruction |
| `total_processed` | `AtomicUsize` | Total submissions completed |
| `avg_wait_ms` | `AtomicUsize` + lock-free CAS EMA loop | Exponential moving average (70/30 weight) |
| Breaker states | `CircuitBreaker::state()` | One each for Redis and API |

