### 11.3 Query Patterns

- Always use parameterized queries (`$1`, `$2`, etc.) — never string concatenation
- `query_as::<_, T>()` for mapping to typed structs (requires `FromRow` derive)
- `query_scalar::<_, T>()` for single-value returns
- `fetch_one` / `fetch_optional` / `fetch_all` based on expected cardinality
- `sqlx::PgPool` connection pool (min 10, max 30 connections in API)

